</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>李家超 FB、IG、微博專頁啟用，分享生活點滴與眾互動</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/07/01/facebookjohnkclee/life-tech/social-network/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=facebookjohnkclee</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 01 Jul 2022 05:55:54 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[社交網絡]]></category><category><![CDATA[Facebook]]></category><category><![CDATA[ig]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1107983</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>李家超今日以政府官員身份展開了社交平臺專頁，包括在 Facebook、Instagram，以及微博。 李家超社 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>李家超今日以政府官員身份展開了社交平臺專頁，包括在 Facebook、Instagram，以及微博。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-01-下午 1.51.10-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107986" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-01-下午 1.51.10-694x540.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="540" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-01-下午 1.51.10-694x540.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-01-下午 1.51.10-1157x900.jpg 1157w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-01-下午 1.51.10-768x598.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-01-下午 1.51.10-1536x1195.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-01-下午 1.51.10-2048x1593.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-01-下午 1.51.19.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107985" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-01-下午 1.51.19-619x580.jpg" alt="" width="619" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-01-下午 1.51.19-619x580.jpg 619w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-01-下午 1.51.19-961x900.jpg 961w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-01-下午 1.51.19-768x719.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-01-下午 1.51.19-1536x1439.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-01-下午 1.51.19.jpg 1610w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 619px" /></a></p><p>李家超社交平臺專頁的背景圖案用上維港日出，以「同為香港開新篇」為口號。在第一篇帖文中李家超指日出充滿生機是新一天的開始，有了新使命作出新嘗試，在社交媒體展開新一頁。社交平臺將用以分享日常工作與生活點滴。他指希望能加強與市民互動。</p><p>第二篇帖文是參與政府就職典禮前的兩個多小時，與其太太準備時的合照。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-01-下午 1.50.42.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107988" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-01-下午 1.50.42-694x493.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="493" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-01-下午 1.50.42-694x493.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-01-下午 1.50.42-1267x900.jpg 1267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-01-下午 1.50.42-768x546.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-01-下午 1.50.42-1536x1091.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-01-下午 1.50.42-2048x1455.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-01-下午 1.51.19.jpg"><br /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-01-下午 1.51.10-scaled.jpg"><br /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-01-下午 1.50.49.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107987" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-01-下午 1.50.49-694x500.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="500" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-01-下午 1.50.49-694x500.jpg 694